data.description: Great Location. One floor renovated, updated ''move-In Ready'' 3 bedroom ranch home located just 1.4 miles to Covell & Craigville Public Beaches.  Ideal location for a year-round, summer, or rental home. Large Living Room with wood burning fireplace and wainscoting on lower one-half of walls & new hardwood floor.  Kitchen has white cabinets and new hardwood floor.  Also brand-new appliances: Frigidaire Gas stove, Refrigerator, & dishwasher.  Separate Dining Room off the kitchen with brand new hardwood floor. Interior just completely painted.  Many brand new Anderson windows. New paved driveway & walk way. Updated full bathroom.  Close to downtown Hyannis.  Ideal for strolling with many shops & restaurants along Main St.  Short drive to  Hy-Line Cruise Ships to Martha's Vineyard and Nantucket. Newer 20x14' wood deck & outdoor shower with a lg. private backyard.  Plenty of space for a boat, kayak, canoes, etc.   Passing 3 bedroom Title V  in hand.
